<div class="col-md-6">
<h3>What is Word Mapper</h3>
<p><strong>Word Mapper</strong> is a web accessible tool that enables students, faculty, and other collaborators to build discontinuous word alignments between two or more texts, so that they can build and share glossaries to aid learning and research.</p>
<br/><br/><br/>
<h3>Reference Implementation</h3>
<p>The bookmarklet above was based on Professor Mark Schiefsky's <a link="http://harvard-atg.github.io/wordmapper/proto/table_2016-02-06.html">original work</a> to develop a word alignment tool.</p>
</div>
