<h3>How to install Word Mapper</h3>
<ol>
	<li>Make sure your browser's Bookmarks Bar is visible.</li><br/>  
	<li>Install <strong>Word Mapper</strong> by dragging <a href="javascript:(function(){document.body.appendChild(document.createElement('script')).src='<%= baseUrl %>/static/js/bookmarklet.js';})();" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">WordMapper</a> to your Bookmarks Bar.</li>
	<br/>
	<img src="/static/images/testfirstimage.png" Alt="bookmarklet">
